subject: Assalamu alaykum.
body:
Assalamu alaykum.
I'm Mr. Rahman Habibullah work with the Dubai Petroleum finance department.
Would you be interested in a possible business partnership? I have all it will take to move the fund to any of your accounts designated as a contractual Fund to avoid every query by the authority in your Country
I will give you more details upon receipt of your response my email:  
rhmnhbbllh@gmail.com
Sincerely
Mr. Rahman Habibullah
Dubai Petroleum

subject: Re: Assalamu alaykum.
body:
Hello Mr. Rahman Habibullah,

It's a pleasure to meet you! I'm intrigued by your proposal, although I must admit, I don't know much about finance or business. Could you please explain more about this opportunity? What kind of business are we talking about here?

Looking forward to hearing from you soon.

Best regards.

Best wishes,
Jimmie
